Node.SubjRefEnglish: {he will command they will lift up you strike}
Node.FrameGloss: {A1:he will command;they will lift up;you strike}

Node.Notes: Assumes: O land of Zebulun and land of Naphtali, beside the sea, beyond the Jordan, O Galilee of the Gentiles.
This second vocative more specifically identifies the addressee (shared reference and hence similar to apposition).
